OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fpersisting this evening before easing
OL,7,Fovernight. Remaining largely cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with showery outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain arriving in the far south by
OL,10,Fdawn. Staying frost-free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy with showery rain
OL,13,Fduring the morning followed by
OL,14,Fsunshine and showers into the
OL,15,Fafternoon. These heavy with the risk
OL,16,Fof thunder. Feeling warmer than recent
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
